1
00:01:05,952 --> 00:01:08,384
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,512 --> 00:01:11,424
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,439
So, you admit planting spies

4
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,959
to watch His Majesty's every move?

5
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:26,319
Your Majesty,
these two eunuchs have confessed.

6
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,840
They privately sold information
from maids to those outside the palace.

7
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:32,239
As for the rumors
about you and His Highness,

8
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:35,079
they just heard from others
and believed it to be true.

9
00:01:35,959 --> 00:01:36,799
Got a name list?

10
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:37,780
Yes.

11
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:54,959
These scoundrels peddle false rumors
as intelligence.

12
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:57,439
Their testimonies cannot be trusted.

13
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:00,280
Wouldn't you agree, Third Uncle?

14
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,079
Your Majesty is wise.

15
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:05,879
However, when I visited the study
to discuss affairs,

16
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:08,400
Your Majesty was indeed seen
together with His Highness.

17
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:11,719
And the study is not a place
for Your Majesty.

18
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:16,680
Prince Xiaoyao handles state affairs,
while I supervise him.

19
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,120
This is His Majesty's decree.

20
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,879
The Empress Dowager can testify for me.

21
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:25,800
His Majesty did inform me of this
before his departure.

22
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:30,159
Your Majesty's inappropriate behavior
inevitably invites slander.

23
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:34,479
I've been loyal and helpful
since I married His Majesty.

24
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:37,800
Now His Majesty risks his life
on the front lines.

25
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:41,919
Instead of serving the nation,
you stir up things here.

26
00:02:42,199 --> 00:02:43,080
Are you loyal then?

27
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,800
Accusing me of impropriety?

28
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,919
You truly aim to blame His Majesty
for poor household governance.

29
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:52,560
So, do you intend to have a new ruler?

30
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:57,599
I swear to heaven
that I'm loyal to His Majesty.

31
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:02,000
By slandering me,
you undermine His Majesty's authority.

32
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:07,759
Is that how you show your loyalty?
Shame on you!

33
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:18,280
- We're wrong. Punish us.
- We're wrong. Punish us.

34
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:44,080
There is such a miraculous place
in the desert.

35
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:46,840
It's clear, warm, and moist.

36
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,879
There are clear seasons here.

37
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,439
Now such heavy snowflakes fall.

38
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:53,960
Beyond the valley, a blizzard must rage.

39
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,919
Huna, thank you.

40
00:03:57,639 --> 00:04:00,759
Before my triumphant return,
I witnessed this wonder.

41
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,960
You're now Queen of Dada.

42
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:08,560
May I borrow your sacred Soul Silk?

43
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:13,479
That is managed by royal shamans.
Right after purging the imperial court,

44
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:15,000
I'll naturally gift it to Chen.

45
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,800
Aren't you curious why I need it?

46
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,040
If I questioned such trivial matters,

47
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,240
as Queen of Dada, I would seem petty.

48
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:30,600
Friendship is always the most precious.

49
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:44,319
Huna, thank you.

50
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,800
I wish to return to Chen immediately.

51
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,759
Unfortunately, you can't.

52
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:05,759
Beyond the valley,
snow has sealed all mountain passes.

53
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,480
What?

54
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,639
You have to stay longer
before saying goodbye.

55
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:15,720
This is the closest place to the moon
in the desert.

56
00:05:15,959 --> 00:05:16,879
It's called Moon Lake.

57
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,720
Perfect for drinking.

58
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:41,319
It's almost the end of the year.

59
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,279
I wonder how lively Chen is
for the new year.

60
00:05:46,439 --> 00:05:47,519
(Xiao Jinyun,)

61
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:50,680
(I fear I'll miss the New Year's Eve.)

62
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:55,160
(May you stay safe. Wait for my return.)

63
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:05,399
(Xu Yu, tonight is New Year's Eve.)

64
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:08,800
(Though the palace bustles,
you're not with me.)

65
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,680
(I'm not happy without you.)

66
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:16,000
(The north is cold. How do you do?)

67
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,600
(Do you have dumplings and fine wine?)

68
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,360
Xiao Jinyun, I promise you.

69
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,360
I'll return safely. I keep my word.

70
00:06:33,850 --> 00:06:36,128
笙ｪSwallows fly south again笙ｪ

71
00:06:36,128 --> 00:06:39,671
笙ｪWe smile at each other
in the setting sun笙ｪ

72
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:43,519
Xiao Jinyun, Happy Spring Festival.

73
00:06:44,479 --> 00:06:46,887
笙ｪOnly gentleness remains笙ｪ

74
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:52,160
Xu Yu, Happy Spring Festival.

75
00:06:54,870 --> 00:06:59,735
笙ｪWe share many memories笙ｪ

76
00:07:01,626 --> 00:07:05,184
笙ｪFrost tints my brows,
while I make a wish笙ｪ

77
00:07:05,184 --> 00:07:07,540
笙ｪAlone holding an umbrella in rain笙ｪ

78
00:07:08,672 --> 00:07:15,153
笙ｪI never closely saw it笙ｪ

79
00:07:15,659 --> 00:07:19,025
笙ｪWorldly joys feel illusory笙ｪ

80
00:07:19,137 --> 00:07:21,841
笙ｪIf you're absent笙ｪ

81
00:07:22,629 --> 00:07:27,697
笙ｪI'll have to shun my desires笙ｪ

82
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,959
(Xu Yu is strong enough
to knock out a bear.)

83
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,759
(Why would she need monthly checkups?)

84
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:42,240
(Since Mother means well, I'll comply.)

85
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,839
(It might improve Xu Yu's image.)

86
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,439
What's wrong?

87
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,399
Well...

88
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,439
Speak.

89
00:07:53,759 --> 00:07:57,120
Empress Dowager,
Her Majesty is pregnant.

90
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:57,920
- What?
- What?

91
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,759
Empress Dowager.

92
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:08,240
Your niece is indeed
two months pregnant.

93
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,560
Leave.

94
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,100
Yes.

95
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,480
Mother, this is impossible.

96
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:29,160
Xu Yu, His Majesty has been at war
for over half a year.

97
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,839
Yet you're two months pregnant.

98
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:35,679
Only your death can quell my wrath.

99
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:40,440
His Majesty forbade you from killing me.

100
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:44,279
Adultery and secret pregnancy
are unforgivable crimes.

101
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:47,440
I'll feed you abortion decoction

102
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,360
out of respect for Marshal Xu's service
in defending the nation.

103
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,960
Otherwise,

104
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:55,759
you'd have been stripped publicly
as a warning to all.

105
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:59,639
I couldn't possibly be pregnant.
This matter is deeply suspicious!

106
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,879
How dare you quibble!

107
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:03,879
I grant you one final chance.

108
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,960
You'd best speak truthfully.

109
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:13,600
Is the child you are carrying Jinming's?

110
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:18,720
No.

111
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:20,600
Then you deserve death all the more.

112
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,480
Are you sure?

113
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:24,480
How would I dare misdiagnose?

114
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,720
Empress Dowager let me take the pulse,

115
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,000
claiming that her niece

116
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:30,600
accidentally fainted in Fengyi Palace

117
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,559
while chatting with Her Majesty.

118
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,480
Only afterward did I realize it.

119
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:37,279
Why would Empress Dowager's niece be
in Fengyi Palace?

120
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,879
The person I examined
must have been Her Majesty.

121
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,080
I saw Her Majesty the other day.

122
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:46,679
Her aura showed no signs of pregnancy.

123
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,720
Someone must
be deliberately framing her.

124
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:51,519
I've already sent people
to check Her Majesty's recent meals.

125
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,039
Someone must have added drugs

126
00:09:53,039 --> 00:09:54,559
to her food, causing a fake pregnancy.

127
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:57,000
Empress Dowager is enraged.
I fear Her Majesty will be punished.

128
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:57,639
Don't panic.

129
00:09:59,460 --> 00:10:01,519
If I can't even
protect my sister-in-law,

130
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,919
I'm useless.

131
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,960
Leave it to me.

132
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:11,120
Grand Preceptor, what should we do?

133
00:10:12,159 --> 00:10:13,159
Trust Jinming.

134
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:26,399
Your Majesty,
allow me to feed you this medicine.

135
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:31,879
Mother, you mustn't!

136
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,480
If I drink this,

137
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:36,720
how could I have His Majesty's child
in the future?

138
00:10:37,679 --> 00:10:39,480
You never should have conceived.

139
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:44,080
On your wedding day,
I replaced Fengyi Palace's incense.

140
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:47,519
The incense contained a sterility drug.

141
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:51,799
Had Jinyun not discovered it
and mercifully removed it,

142
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:53,639
you'd have been barren long ago.

143
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:57,399
(Mother actually did this
behind my back?)

144
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,399
(No!)

145
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:01,360
(I will never allow Xu Yu's body
to be harmed again.)

146
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,559
Force her to drink it.

147
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,440
If you force me, Mother,

148
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,039
I'll end my life right here.

149
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,759
How dare you threaten me!

150
00:11:13,039 --> 00:11:14,159
Before His Majesty returns,

151
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:16,559
if the Empress dies suddenly,

152
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,759
what will happen to the court and harem?

153
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:22,600
Mother, I implore you to reconsider.

154
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:32,279
The Empress has a sudden migraine
and rests in seclusion.

155
00:11:32,639 --> 00:11:33,840
Isn't that a good reason?

156
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,799
Someone! Feed her the medicine.

157
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,299
Mother!

158
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:52,080
The child she is carrying is mine.

159
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,559
You cannot hurt her.

160
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:55,860
What?

161
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:57,919
You...

162
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:04,000
Jinming, how could you betray Jinyun?

163
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,240
When he returns, you'll learn the truth.

164
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:12,360
If you insist on executing her,
I can die for her.

165
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,039
You...

166
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,360
Virtuous Consort is so kind.

167
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,799
Your Majesty is now confined
to the Cold Palace,

168
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:43,759
but she specifically asked me
to deliver food to you.

169
00:12:57,376 --> 00:13:00,282
(Annotation)

170
00:13:05,018 --> 00:13:06,874
(Save this place.)

171
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,159
Great calligraphy, Your Majesty.

172
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,360
(Th-This is His Majesty's handwriting.)

173
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,240
(I'm sure about it.)

174
00:13:28,679 --> 00:13:29,879
You're trying to poison me?

175
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,919
I'm not, Your Majesty! Spare me, please!

176
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,919
Are you hearing yourself right now?

177
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:41,000
Your Majesty's voice lives in my mind.

178
00:13:41,639 --> 00:13:45,799
Thus, from your speech and handwriting,

179
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,039
I deduced it.

180
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,840
Though I'm ignorant of the full story,

181
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,000
I...

182
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:54,519
I could never mistake Your Majesty.

183
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,159
You know what?

184
00:13:56,799 --> 00:14:00,080
Knowing too much is very dangerous.

185
00:14:01,039 --> 00:14:04,960
My family and I
depend entirely on Your Majesty.

186
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:08,919
If Your Majesty is safe,
I am willing to die.

187
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:16,679
Keep your mouth shut then.

188
00:14:17,039 --> 00:14:18,000
As you command.

189
00:14:18,759 --> 00:14:20,000
Now tell me.

190
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,240
Who seeks to poison me?

191
00:14:47,290 --> 00:14:52,474
笙ｪParting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon笙ｪ

192
00:14:53,210 --> 00:14:57,773
笙ｪBrewing a pot of bygone years笙ｪ

193
00:14:59,098 --> 00:15:04,513
笙ｪChill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul笙ｪ

194
00:15:05,082 --> 00:15:09,626
笙ｪDrunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned笙ｪ

195
00:15:10,266 --> 00:15:15,530
笙ｪIf not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream笙ｪ

196
00:15:15,898 --> 00:15:21,575
笙ｪReturning to drift
through the mortal world笙ｪ

197
00:15:21,914 --> 00:15:23,930
笙ｪLike her, like me, like you笙ｪ

198
00:15:24,122 --> 00:15:27,866
笙ｪHairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets笙ｪ

199
00:15:28,442 --> 00:15:33,114
笙ｪFate laid bare my deepest thoughts笙ｪ

200
00:15:33,658 --> 00:15:35,418
笙ｪLike vows, like remorse, like love笙ｪ

201
00:15:35,738 --> 00:15:39,354
笙ｪLoving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting笙ｪ

202
00:15:39,601 --> 00:15:45,128
笙ｪTell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more笙ｪ
